<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-bored-scared-frightened-to-death">be bored / scared / frightened to death</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>无聊得 / 怕得要死：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was scared to death of what might happen next.
她对接下来可能发生的事怕得要死。</p></div></div>